function Start()
	
	local sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD

	if Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
		sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD_HEROIC
	end
	
	Events.SpawnRewardChest(CHEST_LOCATION, sChest)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	if Hydra.ActorGetMonsterFamily(idActorKilled) == "Fallen" then
		Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idActorKilled, 2)
	end
end

local function spawnWave(index)

	Hydra.Wait(0.3)
	
	if (index == N_WAVES_MAX) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, SFX_MAJOR_WAVE)
	else
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, SFX_MINOR_WAVE)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	
	if index <= N_WAVES_MAX then
		for i, spawnerID in pairs(tWaves[index]) do
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(spawnerID) then 
				Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(spawnerID, false)
				Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(spawnerID, PSAG_WAVE)
			end
		end
	else
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "Spawners_Wave_Repeat")
	end

	if index % 2 == 0 then --Only trigger the champion spawners on even numbered waves		
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "Champions")
	end
end

-- ======= CONSTANTS =======
ID_THIS_QUEST = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

--	Quest Constants
PSAG_WAVE = "LE_MonsterWaves_Wave"
N_WAVES_MAX = 5

-- Spawners
tWaves = {}
for i = 1, N_WAVES_MAX do
	tWaves[i] = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, "Spawners_Wave_0"..tostring(i))
end
